<h2 style="color:#1B587B;">News</h2>
8/23/2011 - <b>Bcrypt!</b></br>
<p>Mooncoin puts serious thought into the security of our users, so we have took enabled bcrypt for password encryption. This method is much better then a SHA-256 + Salt. Just remember to update your passwords on the user page!</p>
